org.neuroph.core.data

Class DataSetRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neuroph.core.data.DataSetRow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DataSetRow
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class represents single data row in a data set. It has input and desired output for supervised learning rules. It can also be used only with input for unsupervised learning rules.
    Author:
    Zoran Sevarac
